TextEng: Who are you?
What is this place?
What are you doing here?
Who you be?
What this place be?
What you be doing here?
How do you know that?
Nope. That's not my name.
How you know?
You make mistake. That not be me name.
Text: 너 틀렸어. 그거 내 이름 아니야.

TextEng: What kinds of things do you discuss and learn about?
What do you mean 'challenge' nature?
What do you mean, they've gone missing?
Yes, well... nature bores me. Goodbye.
Text: 뭐, 그런데... 자연은 지루하네요. 안녕히 계세요.

TextEng: What you talk and learn 'bout?
What you mean 'challenge' nature?
What you mean some missing?
Me get easily bored. We no talk no more. Bye bye.
Text: 나 쉽게 지루해져. 나 이제 얘기 안 해. 안녕.

TextEng: Thank you.
Too late.
You mean rangers and druids are being attacked?
I guess they finally get to see what everyone experiences in the wild.
Text: 모두가 야생에서 경험하는 일을 드디어 겪게 됐네요.

TextEng: You say rangers and druids no be safe no more?
Text: 너 말하는 거 순찰자랑 드루이드 이제 안전하지 않다는 거야?

TextEng: That what it always be like when me camp in woods.
Text: 나 숲에서 야영할 때 항상 그래.

TextEng: What is wrong with the Spirit?
What is the Spirit of the Wood?
What be spook in trees?
What be wrong with Spirit?
So what is wrong with it then?
I don't understand that at all.
So what be wrong then?
Me not know what you mean.
I think so, but then what is wrong with the Spirit?
Text: 그런 것 같긴 한데, 그럼 정령에게 무슨 문제가 있는 거죠?

TextEng: No. I still don't understand.
Maybe. So what wrong with Spirit?
Nope. Me not need brain tell hand what to do.
Text: 아니. 나 뇌가 손한테 뭐 하라고 말할 필요 없어.

TextEng: Oh, okay.
I think I can handle that.
What's in it for me if I decide to do this?
I think I'm a little busy right now.
Me do it.
What you pay for me to do this?
Text: 나 이거 하면 너 뭐 줄 거야?

TextEng: Me got other things to do.
What did you mean when you said some of you went missing?
Text: 여러분 중 일부가 실종됐다고 하셨을 때 무슨 뜻이었죠?

TextEng: What you mean when you say some folk go missing?
Text: 사람들 실종됐다고 말했을 때 무슨 뜻이야?

TextEng: I swear I shall do my best to save the Wood.
Text: 숲을 구하기 위해 최선을 다할 것을 맹세합니다.

TextEng: Yeah, yeah, enough with the speeches. I said I would take the job.
Text: 네, 네, 연설은 그만하세요. 일 받겠다고 했잖아요.

TextEng: Maybe you should find someone else. I'm rather busy.
Text: 다른 사람 찾는 게 나을 것 같은데요. 전 좀 바빠서요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You shall find I am always very committed - to gold.
Me swear me do good job!
Why you keep going on and on and on. Me say me take job.
Text: 왜 계속 말하고 또 말하고 또 말해. 나 일 받는다고 했어.

TextEng: Me not want job that bad. You get someone else.
Text: 나 그렇게까지 일 원하지 않아. 너 다른 사람 구해.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me committed to get paid. You pay, me do.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 돈 받는 데 헌신적이야. 너 주면, 나 해.

TextEng: What are the names of the missing druids?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Maybe you could pay me something in advance?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 혹시 선불로 좀 주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: That's all I need. Farewell.
Text: 필요한 건 다 들었어요. 안녕히 계세요.

TextEng: What be druid's names who be gone?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You give me some gold now, maybe?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 너 지금 금화 좀 줘, 어때?

TextEng: That all me need. Bye bye.
Text: 나 필요한 거 다 들었어. 안녕.

TextEng: Tell me what you need assistance with again.
Text: 다시 한번 뭘 도와드려야 하는지 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: I would like to help you.
Nothing. Goodbye.
What you need done again?
Me want help you.
Goodbye.
What are the names of the druids?
I think I have found one of your druids.
Text: 드루이드 중 한 명을 찾은 것 같아요.

TextEng: I have cured the Spirit of the Wood.
The Spirit of the Wood is dead.
What be names of lost druids?
Me found druid.
Me cure Spirit of Wood.
Spirit of Wood be dead.
No. Goodbye.
Is this one of your druids?
Text: 이 사람이 당신네 드루이드 중 한 명인가요?

TextEng: This be druid, yuh?
I am happy to have been of service. Thank you for your generosity.
Text: 도움이 돼서 기쁩니다. 후한 보상 감사드립니다.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I had to die to save your precious Spirit! I think such a sacrifice should be worth a little more than 500 gold.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 당신의 소중한 정령을 구하려고 죽었어요! 그런 희생이라면 금화 500개보다는 좀 더 가치가 있어야 한다고 봅니다.

TextEng: You will give me more than 500 gold pieces or maybe I'll set fire to your precious forest!
Text: 금화 500개보다 더 주셔야 할 텐데요. 안 그러면 당신의 소중한 숲에 불을 지를지도 몰라요!

TextEng: Restoring the balance of nature is reward enough for me. Give the 500 gold pieces to the poor instead.
Text: 자연의 균형을 회복하는 것만으로도 충분한 보상입니다. 금화 500개는 가난한 이들에게 주세요.

TextEng: Me be glad job done. Thanks for gold.
Text: 나 일 끝나서 기뻐. 금화 고마워.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me died to do job. Me think me life worth more than 500 gp.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 일 하느라 죽었어. 나 생각에 내 목숨은 금화 500개보다 가치 있어.

TextEng: You give me more than 500 gold pieces or maybe me burn down whole forest.
Text: 너 금화 500개보다 더 줘야 해. 안 그러면 나 숲 다 태워버릴지도 몰라.

TextEng: Job need done, so me do. Me no need you gold.
Text: 일 해야 하니까, 나 했어. 나 너 금화 필요 없어.

TextEng: I am sorry for nature's loss, but there were no other choices open to me.
Text: 자연의 손실에 대해 유감입니다만, 다른 선택지가 없었어요.

TextEng: Hey, you win some, you lose some. Either way I still expect to get paid.
Text: 뭐, 이길 때도 있고 질 때도 있죠. 어쨌든 여전히 돈은 받을 거예요.

TextEng: Me sad that had to kill Spirit, but me had no choice.
Text: 나 정령 죽여야 해서 슬퍼, 하지만 나 선택 없었어.

TextEng: What you complain for? Spirit no make animals attack no more. Now you pay me.
Text: 뭘 불평해? 정령 이제 동물들 공격하게 안 해. 이제 너 나한테 돈 줘.

TextEng: I understand. Please accept my apology and my gratitude for what you could give.
Text: 이해합니다. 제 사과와 주실 수 있는 것에 대한 감사를 받아주세요.

TextEng: Saving the forest is more important than a reward. Take all of the gold and do what you can.
Text: 숲을 구하는 게 보상보다 중요합니다. 금화 다 가져가서 할 수 있는 걸 하세요.

TextEng: No! We had a deal and you had better stick with it or else!
Text: 안 돼요! 우리 거래했고 지키는 게 좋을 거예요. 안 그러면!

TextEng: Me sorry. Me thank you for gold and hope you save forest.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 금화 고마워하고 너 숲 구하길 바래.

TextEng: You need save forest. Me let you keep all gold to help.
Text: 너 숲 구해야 해. 나 너한테 금화 다 줄게 도와.

TextEng: You pay me 500 gold now, or else.
Text: 너 지금 금화 500개 줘, 안 그러면.

TextEng: Is there anything that I can do as a druid to assist the grove?
There be stuff me do as druid here?
Text: 나 드루이드로서 여기서 할 일 있어?

TextEng: Is there anything else that I can do to assist the grove?
There be stuff me do for grove?
Text: 내가 성소 위해 할 일 있어?

TextEng: Where were the druids last seen?
Where druids be seen last?
